Description: Lua 5.5 scripting engine module for Valkey
 A Lua 5.5 scripting engine module for Valkey that provides EVAL,
 EVALSHA, FUNCTION, and SCRIPT commands backed by an embedded Lua 5.5
 interpreter. Uses a per-user architecture where each authenticated user
 gets their own pair of lua_State instances, eliminating the need for
 readonly-table protection.
